The Wikipedia Library

Adam Matthew

Adam Matthew Digital is a subsidiary of SAGE Publications that focuses on publishing databases of primary sources and accompanying supporting material. For this partnership, we will have access to all 53 of their databases that allow access to a range of collections relevant to major topics in American and World History. A full list of collections can be found here.

Userbox

Add {{Wikipedia:Adam Matthew/Userbox}} to your userboxes! This helps us share our project with other experienced users.
